# CI/CD Team Pod Owner Routing
# This file drives both PR review assignment and IssueOps triage routing.
# One edit here updates all downstream behavior — PR reviews and issue routing.
# Format: path  @github-handle
#
# To update a pod owner:
#   1. Replace the @handle below
#   2. Commit to main
#   3. All subsequent triage routing updates automatically

# ── Vertical Pod Owners ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.github/verticals/datadog/           @pod-owner-datadog
.github/verticals/artifactory/       @pod-owner-artifactory
.github/verticals/github-platform/   @pod-owner-github
.github/verticals/jira-wiki/         @pod-owner-jira
.github/verticals/tfe/               @pod-owner-tfe
.github/verticals/gitlab-pipelines/  @pod-owner-gitlab

# ── Workflow Files — Team Lead Review Required ───────────────────────────────
.github/workflows/                   @team-lead
.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/              @team-lead
.github/copilot/                     @team-lead

# ── Default Ownership ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*                                    @team-lead
